  "title": "Student Care Teacher - Tampines",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Location - Tampines</li><li>Private Student Care Centre</li><li>Cozy and Supportive Working Environment</li><li>Monday - Friday (10AM - 7PM)</li><li>Training Provided</li></ul><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise and ensure the well-being, safety, and discipline of students in the student care centre</li><li>Provide guidance and support to students in completing their school homework and assignments</li><li>Facilitate learning and enrichment activities that promote character development and life skills</li><li>Conduct activities and lessons with a focus on <strong>English language</strong>, <strong>Chinese language</strong>, <strong>Mathematics</strong> and <strong>Science</strong> depending on teaching strength</li><li>Work collaboratively with colleagues to maintain a positive and supportive environment</li><li>Communicate with parents/guardians on students’ progress when necessary</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum <strong>Diploma</strong> or <strong>Degree </strong>in any related field</li><li>Strong proficiency in <strong>English</strong> for English-focused teaching and <strong>Chinese</strong> for Chinese-focused teaching, to guide students effectively</li><li>Genuine interest and passion for working with children</li><li>Good interpersonal and classroom management skills</li></ul><p>Interested Candidates, please send your latest resume to <strong>eeting@talentsatwork.sg</strong> or WhatsApp me at <strong>86872681</strong></p><p>Ee Ting (R25127402)<br />Talents@Work Pte Ltd (21C0501)</p>",
